 | 3 - Favicon set | `favicon.ico`, `index.html`, `sw.js`, `CODEX-REPORT.md` | PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js` | Added 16/32/48 favicon, inserted ICO link before SVG icon link, added favicon to `APP_SHELL`, and bumped cache from v7 to v8. SVG raster tooling was unavailable, so ICO was generated from the matching 512px PNG mark. |
 | 4 - Store screenshots | `store/01_track_your_album.png`, `store/02_find_the_best_trade.png`, `store/03_offers_not_accidents.png`, `store/04_confirm_the_handover_together.png`, `store/05_finish_the_album_together.png`, `CODEX-REPORT.md` | PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js` | Captured real `index.html?demo=1` screens at 390x844 in the in-app browser, scaled them 3x, and framed them on `assets/15_store_screenshot_background.webp` at 1290x2796. No app-shell changes were needed because store screenshots are not cached. |
 | 5 - Light-theme contrast sweep | `index.html`, `CODEX-REPORT.md` | PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js` | Added light-only contrast overrides for app chrome, progress cards, open team/sticker surfaces, and swap cards. Before/after screenshots captured at `/private/tmp/sticker-swap-light-before.png` and `/private/tmp/sticker-swap-light-after.png`. |
+| 6 - Accessibility sweep | `index.html`, `CODEX-REPORT.md` | PASS - `node scripts/qa-check.js` | Added visible focus styling, converted wishlist stars to named buttons with `aria-pressed`, converted filter chips to buttons, made team headers keyboard-toggleable with `aria-expanded`, and named the nudge button. Browser check found 115 wishlist buttons, 0 span wishlist stars, and 51 keyboard team headers. |
